% B6 with stack recording disabled.
% B6 - B6_norec = cost of three toArray() calls in raiseerror
% (ostack + estack + dstack deep copies into $errordict on every
% error). Shallow estack/ostack here -- variants B6b/B6c stress
% the depth dimension.
errordict /recordstacks false put
tic 1000000 { { /test /Bench raiseerror } stopped { handleerror } if } repeat toc ==
quit
